---
// About section — two-column: text left, SVG terminal illustration right
---

<section class="section about" id="about" aria-label="About Lorenz">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about__grid fade-in">

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="about__text">
        <h2 class="section-heading">About Me</h2>

        <div class="about__education-badge">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5-10-5z" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M6 12v5c0 2.21 2.686 4 6 4s6-1.79 6-4v-5" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          BSIT Software Development&nbsp;&nbsp;·&nbsp;&nbsp;MMDC / Mapúa Malayan Colleges
        </div>

        <p class="about__para">
          For over seven years I led operations and learning &amp; development programs in the BPO industry —
          managing performance governance across 400+ agents, designing training programs, and building the
          kind of process documentation that actually gets followed. That career taught me to think in
          systems, communicate clearly across levels, and ship results under pressure.
        </p>

        <p class="about__para">
          The pivot to software development wasn't a break from that work — it was the next logical step.
          I was already deep into data dashboards, workflow automation, and tooling. What I wanted was to
          move from <em>using</em> software to <em>building</em> it. So in 2023 I enrolled in BSIT Software
          Development at MMDC / Mapúa Malayan Colleges, and I've been writing code ever since.
        </p>

        <p class="about__para">
          I build with Java (desktop, Swing), MySQL, and plain web technologies. I care about clean
          architecture, readable code, and software that actually solves the problem it's supposed to solve.
          Currently looking for junior developer roles, freelance projects, and interesting collaborations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SVG terminal illustration -->
      <div class="about__illustration" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg
          class="terminal-svg"
          viewBox="0 0 380 260"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          role="img"
          aria-label="Code terminal illustration"
        >
          <!-- Window chrome -->
          <rect width="380" height="260" rx="12" fill="#1E293B"/>
          <!-- Title bar -->
          <rect width="380" height="40" rx="12" fill="#0F172A"/>
          <rect y="28" width="380" height="12" fill="#0F172A"/>
          <!-- Traffic lights -->
          <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="6" fill="#EF4444"/>
          <circle cx="38" cy="20" r="6" fill="#F59E0B"/>
          <circle cx="56" cy="20" r="6" fill="#22C55E"/>
          <!-- Title bar text -->
          <text x="190" y="25" font-family="monospace" font-size="11" fill="#64748B" text-anchor="middle">portfolio — terminal</text>
          <!-- Code lines -->
          <!-- Line 1: prompt -->
          <text x="20" y="72" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#22C55E">$</text>
          <text x="32" y="72" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#94A3B8">java -version</text>
          <!-- Line 2: output -->
          <text x="20" y="92" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#64748B">java 25.0.2 2025-01-21 LTS</text>
          <!-- Line 3: blank prompt -->
          <text x="20" y="116" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#22C55E">$</text>
          <text x="32" y="116" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#94A3B8">git log --oneline -3</text>
          <!-- Line 4-6: git log -->
          <text x="20" y="136" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#A78BFA">a3f91c2</text>
          <text x="80" y="136" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#94A3B8">feat: add RBAC permission layer</text>
          <text x="20" y="152" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#A78BFA">7d04be1</text>
          <text x="80" y="152" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#94A3B8">fix: MySQL connection pool</text>
          <text x="20" y="168" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#A78BFA">1c9aef0</text>
          <text x="80" y="168" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#94A3B8">init: project scaffold</text>
          <!-- Line 7: new prompt -->
          <text x="20" y="192" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#22C55E">$</text>
          <text x="32" y="192" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#94A3B8">npm run build</text>
          <!-- Line 8: build output -->
          <text x="20" y="212" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#38BDF8">▶ astro build</text>
          <text x="20" y="228" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#22C55E">✔ Complete!</text>
          <text x="108" y="228" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#64748B">built in 1.24s</text>
          <!-- Blinking cursor -->
          <rect x="20" y="240" width="8" height="14" fill="#2563EB" rx="1">
            <animate attributeName="opacity" values="1;0;1" dur="1.1s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
          </rect>
        </svg>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about__education-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__para {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__para em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__illustration {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .terminal-svg {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.35);
    transition: transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  .terminal-svg:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .terminal-svg:hover {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .about__illustration {
      order: -1;
    }

    .terminal-svg {
      max-width: 340px;
    }
  }
</style>
